      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/britain-s-ultra-rich-map-out-plans-to-escape-non-dom-taxes-after-labour-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，巴西姆·海达尔已经拥有了英国超级富豪的所有典型特征：一架湾流喷气式飞机、豪华游艇和与中东皇室为邻的豪宅。]]></description>
